{
  "texts": [
    "The model * persona interaction is essential because persona effects vary dramatically by model.",
    "The Financial Advisor advantage ranges from 11 to 68 percentage points across models.Three key methodological choices ensure valid inference.",
    "First, we use clustered standard errors at the conversation level [43] because the four sequential probes form a single conversation, violating independence assumptions.",
    "Second, we report effects as percentage point differences rather than odds ratios for interpretability [2,25].",
    "Third, we emphasize effect sizes over p-values given the large sample size of 19,200 observations, which provides enormous statistical power [8]."
  ]
}